attributes.title: Don’t download. Waste of time.
attributes.review: I should have listen to the reviews because this app takes FOREVER to download. Even when it finished, I couldn’t make my account because this app kept crashing! What a disappointment. I would rate 0 stars if I could.

attributes.title: WORST APP EVER!!!!
attributes.review: I literally just downloaded the app and it made my my CRASH!!! My phone has NEVER did that before. I tried to delete it and my phone literally went out and I had to pay $150 to have my phone to come on then for $100 for apple to delete the app. For someone who received a small loan of a million dollars you sure have bad taste in apps.

attributes.title: Gen Z don’t go down without a fight.
attributes.review: This app is garbage y’all know this. Instead download tik tok much more entertaining and helpful!

attributes.title: Could be better
attributes.review: As soon as a opened the app my phone completely shut down and would not turn back on for 20 minutes. I have reason to believe that Trump himself has made this happen as he is likely frustrated with my decision to wear a green and yellow shirt when he has made it very clear that he only tolerates red and orange clothing. I am very unhappy that he has taken his frustrations out on my brand new samsung HX 56 phone. I was initially planning on voting for trump in the upcoming 2020 election but after downloading this disappointing app I will have no choice but to put my vote elsewhere 😔

attributes.title: Fitting: Worst App for the Worst President.
Worst App...
attributes.review:
I’m sorry, but there are a lot of ways to spread news and messages out to the public, but this is not it!
I recently downloaded the app to gain more knowledge of what is going on in the world and our society and this has been the worst decision I have made. Too many unimportant messages and it’s crazy.. even upon signing up I don’t feel safe. 
Too much of your info is put out on display and I just feel overall disappointed with this app.
